    "description_html": "<div>\n                Designed to deliver lightweight speed, superior breathability, and responsive cushioning, the Wave Strike is engineered to match the demands of today’s most dynamic players. A translucent mesh upper enhances airflow and flexibility while also creating a sleek, modern look. Underfoot, MIZUNO ENERZY foam in the heel combines with a U4icX strobel lasting board and POWNCE midsole to deliver next-level comfort and responsiveness. The D-Flex Groove supports explosive lateral movement, while the X10 outsole provides durability and reliable grip on every pivot and slide. Built on a comfort last for a more relaxed fit on and off the court, the Wave Strike AC is ready for both competition and everyday wear.\n            </div>",
