    "description_html": "<div>\n                Designed for the active tennis or pickleball player, the ALL-NEW <b>WAVE EXCEED COURT AC</b> expands on the legacy of the Wave Exceed Light series, offering the utmost in lightweight, cushioned comfort. No longer does a player need to choose between comfort and weight, as the Wave Exceed Court is one of the lightest and most comfortable shoes on the market. The next generation of MIZUNO ENERZY, ENERZY NXT - the lightest and most responsive ENERZY material yet - is integrated throughout the entire midsole to deliver explosive speed, plush cushioning and elevated energy return. An updated MIZUNO WAVE plate and the addition of D-Flex Groove technology increase lateral stability without added weight. A comfort last with a spacious width, along with an engineered mesh upper, combine to supply players of all levels with a premium level of comfort, flexibility and speed.\n            </div>",
